Dior Autumn-Winter 2021-2022 Haute Couture Streetstyle exclusively for 24Fashion TV.



What do you think about the looks of front row guests from the show Dior Autumn-Winter 2021-2022 Haute Couture?


Leonie Hanne

Yana Rudkovskaya

Xenia Adonts

Lena Situations

Justyna Czerniak 

Giovanna Battaglia Engelbert

Christine Alexandra Chiu 

Carlotta Rubaltelli 


Photojournalist: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad

Production: Fashionview @fashionview.eu for 24Fashion.tv
